alwaysApply: true
---

polars 的日期筛选，结合pandas来进行

例如

```python
import pandas as pd
import polars as pl

start_date = '2025-01-01'
end_date = '20251231'

df = pl.read_csv(...)
df = df.filter(
    (pl.col("date") >= pl.lit(pd.to_datetime(start_date))) & 
    (pl.col("date") <= pl.lit(pd.to_datetime(end_date)))
)

```